Location Overview:
The Moorebank industrial precinct is located approximately 27kms west of Sydney CBD, within close proximity to the M5/Westlink M7 interchange, providing excellent access to the major road network including the Hume and Cumberland Highways.

Benefits of location:
* Ease of access to all metropolitan areas
* Minimal time to the proposed Moorebank International Port
* Prime location for access to CBD, Port Botany and interstate highways

Property features:
* Main office: comprises a two storey building of brick construction. The majority of the amenities and facilities are incorporated within the office area including a large lunchroom, which leads to an external break out area.
* Warehouse: construction of the warehouse is predominately metal clad with various internal heights. Highlights:
* Building area: 14,958sqm*
* Large pharmaceutical manufacturing & distribution facility
* High yielding asset
* Long term lease in place
